data.description: A FULLY REMODELED CONTEMPORARY STUNNER!... with views of DTLA, city and ocean in the prestigious Wilshire Manning on Wilshire corridor. Upon entry you are greeted to an expansive open floorplan conveniently accompanied by a spacious living room, dining area, family room/den, open concept kitchen w/ Thermador appliances, waterfall center island, separate service entrance, powder room, laundry room, smart home technology and much more. Sliding glass doors in the living room open and transition you to a balcony with south-west facing epic views away from the Wilshire noise. Stroll to your impressive primary bedroom with walk-in closet, a wall closet and a large amazing bathroom with dual vanities. The sizeable second bedroom also offers a walk-in closet and a gorgeous ensuite bathroom. Both bedrooms offer unobstructed views of the city. The unit provides two parking spaces that are side by side with an electric charging station.  Building amenities include, 24-hour concierge, doorman, valet, pool, spa, sauna, gym, conference room and a banquet room. Centrally located with close proximity to UCLA, 405 freeway, Century City and Westwood Village. For those looking for a move-in condition, meticulously remodeled contemporary condominium on the Wilshire corridor with views, your golden opportunity has come! Don't miss out.
